1.0.0.name: wordpress/wp-formbuilder
1.0.0.description:
WPEden Form Builder Plugin packed with all required features you will need to build a form. Unlike other form builder plugin it avoided all unnecessary complexity and will give you a easy and comfortable option for building your form using drag and drop method. No HTML or CSS knowledge required.

Yes! It is totally "DRAG and DROP"

Features

  • Drag and Drop Builder
  • No HTML or CSS knowledge required
  • re-Captcha field integrated
  • Integrated form validator
  • Custom Post Type
  • Custom email notification
  • Usable with any theme
